ed since the last report:**\\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\\n\\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, blocker appeared, task completed), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\\n\\nFormat:\\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\\n\\nChanges detected:\\n• [list of actual changes]\\n\\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\\n• Active sessions: N\\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\\n• Blockers: none / [list blockers]\\n\\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 15th, 2026 - 1:10 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-15 01:10 UTC\\n\\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776215447550,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"e0b0880d\",\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me check the sessions list and compare against the last known state in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_evxm7ae5u4z7_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"kinds\": [\n                  \"agent\",\n                  \"task\"\n                ],\n                \"limit\": 20,\n                \"messageLimit\": 3\n              }\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_evxm7ae5u4z7_2\",\n              \"name\": \"read\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \