daily briefing cron finished around 23:16 UTC. There's a telegram group session that I'm still calculating the duration for.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"I can see the sessions. Excluding the current cron session (`cron:e7885813`), there are 5 other active sessions. Sending the status report to Lead.\\n\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_satqvhij0xt1_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_send\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"sessionKey\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n                \"message\": \"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 01:04 UTC 15 Apr\\n\\nActive sessions: 5\\n• cron:ed2d0b5d (QLHV 5p): running — 5p progress monitor — ~13m\\n• cron:6f3323ef (DTLX 5p): running — 5p progress monitor DTLX — ~9h 51m\\n• cron:e7885813 (Status): running — Agent Status to Lead — now\\n• telegram:direct:6053576134 (Lead): running — direct comm channel — ~29m\\n• telegram:group:-5163901258 (Group): running — group monitoring — ~10m\\n\\nPipeline: HEALTHY ✅\\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\\n• Blockers: none\\n\\n— Orbis 🌐\"\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 8588,\n            \"output\": 926,\n            \"totalTokens\": 23666,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13849,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 303,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776215075908,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e172468b638e6eb6f7b48d32b8dd4\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"ea5b59df\",\n            \"seq\": 4\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": 